title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell.
OB: When exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown. The exception occurs in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' method.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data is exported without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Export data in two tables.
